location.fullValue: Heritage Village Of Palm Beach Lakes

data.description: Beautifull townhouse in the highly desirable community of Sandalwood Lakes, centrally located. These 2 bedrooms, 21/2 bathroom with tile flooring throughout the first floor and laminate on the second floor. Kitchen have been updated with new stainless-steel appliances and quartz on the counter.  Downstairs the half bathroom includes full size Samsung washer and dryer. Walk-in closet in master room. Both master and guess room have their own balcony. Patio is fully fenced to enjoy your peaceful. Close to downtown, airport, malls, restaurants and more.
